    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every curve is polished to perfection, and the interior still has that wonderful fresh scent. There might be a tiny, invisible speck if you look with a magnifying glass, but to anyone with eyes, she\u2019s an absolute dream. Come take a look\u2014you\u2019ll fall in love just like I did!",
