      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It honestly breaks my heart a little to let this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the magic. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with only the finest detailing. It\u2019s in truly breathtaking condition, looking and smelling just like it did the day it left the showroom floor. Aside from the tiniest, nearly invisible mark from a single weekend cruise, she is practically flawless and drives like a dream. I'd love for you to come by, grab a coffee, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one. You won't find another one kept with this much love!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
