      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously preserved E46 M3, a true driver\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54 inline-six. This unit has undergone a comprehensive top-end refresh, including a bespoke VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement to mitigate factory torsional stress. The compression across all six cylinders remains within tight tolerances, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. Suspension geometry is dialed in with upgraded bushings and a refreshed dampening profile for surgical turn-in. No deferred maintenance; the throttle response is telepathic and the shift linkage is crisp. This is a concourse-ready example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
